Hi dice! hope you are reading this... I have some update ideas that I think could greatly improve the original trilogy even further, including skins and reinforcements. To start this off Im going to list what stormtrooper skins I would like to see in-game. First would be the Shore Trooper, second would be the Patrol trooper, shadow trooper, and the shock trooper. Now these are the reinforcements.
The Range Trooper. Class: Enforcer. Base Health: 200. His gun would fire in bursts of 2, dealing 50 damage with each shot with little to no recoil, but as a trade of would have a long(ish) cool-down. When zoomed in, he fires both shots at a time that have greater accuracy and more controlled splash damage, dealing 100 damage. His first ability would be called precision blast, essentially he would charge up his blaster to release a high damaging projectile that would have a large splash effect and would disable all abilities and keep them from recharging. His second ability would be strength in numbers, this would boost his and any amount of teammates in a small radius health and movement speed, the more people in the abilities area, the stronger the health and movement speed buff would be. With his final ability it would be called imperial might. This would basically be a very strong impact grenade that would make enemies take more damage provide a slowing effect in there movement speed. His passive ability would be magnetized boots. This would let him walk up slanted slopes more easily, and would not be effected by abilities that would would otherwise sen troopers flying. I also have ideas for a Rebel Commando.
